Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.71,0:00:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard! Where the hell did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I go into the alley,\NI'll only get cornered.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.88,0:00:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guess I'll head back out for now, and—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.35,0:00:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.56,0:00:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't cause a commotion now\Nand risk getting noticed by the perpetrator.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.48,0:00:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone chasing you, by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.86,0:00:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're in trouble, I can help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.78,0:00:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met somewhere before?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.79,0:00:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think this is the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But what about your pursuers?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.66,0:00:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't get going,\Nthey're going to catch up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.58,0:00:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is, I'd like to avoid\Nany trouble if I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then come on! This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't tell me this girl is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.02,0:01:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}a Strega?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:42.08,ArcName,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Battle Song
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.45,0:02:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since we've come this far,\NI guess we should be in the clear for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I really owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.63,0:02:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So? Why were they chasing you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.96,0:02:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did they rip you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.46,0:02:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:02:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you don't have to tell me\Nif you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.35,0:03:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're planning to head back,\NI'd wait a little longer if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With Rotlicht being\Nkind of on edge, and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:10.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since there's a Festa\Nunderway right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The police have been cracking down\Nway harder than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:21.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So the mafia running Rotlicht\Nare acting pretty paranoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.70,0:03:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that's the case,\Nmaybe I should look elsewhere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.62,0:03:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to thank you properly if I could,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I just don't have the time right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, it's all right.\NDon't worry about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato Amagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at those speedy reflexes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder\Nyou're a Phoenix Festa finalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, I'm a little devastated\Nthat you'd be so wary of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aside from the fact\Nthat you're already a celebrity...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should work\Non your disguise more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally obvious that it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not like I helped you\Nbecause you're famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But then why would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who wouldn't help someone\Nin their time of need?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And besides,\Nyou didn't strike me as a villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. After you saved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a nice guy, aren't you?\NRight, it's not like I—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about giving\Nyour pursuers a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, was it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.85,0:04:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The bastard who's been\Nlooking for somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My guys would be interested\Nto hear about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're coming with me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew you'd actually\Nchase him all the way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:48.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?\NThere's a woman here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about happy accidents!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, that really motivates me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to resist to your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, it would be such a bore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up a second!\NThis girl has nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably wasting your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, he's the type who puts\Nhis own hobbies over his work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:18.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Former Jie Long Seventh Institute Rank #7,\NNguyen of the Twin Snakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.07,0:05:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.49,0:05:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, how awesome is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that a Lindwurs Festa\Nsemifinalist would be reduced
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to serving as a runner for the mafia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.75,0:05:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.35,0:05:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the best you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:05:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'm gonna go for broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you were still in your prime,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this wouldn't have gone so smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right... By the way,\Nare you looking for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:30.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's what I heard\Nthat guy mention just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just might be able to help you out\Nwith that... What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Help me out? You?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But first...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:43.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we go somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to take up your time\Nwhen you seem to be in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:06:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm the one who should be sorry\Nfor dragging you into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I think I might be starting\Nto figure you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:04.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Figure me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even when you're in trouble yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you're a kind-hearted person\Nwho can be considerate to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.18,0:07:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you also try to carry\Nthe load by yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and you can't bring yourself\Nto rely on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But during your\Nsemifinal match yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you did lean on Riessfeld, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.98,0:07:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You two really looked\Nlike a team out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty perceptive, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.78,0:07:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then, can you tell me\Nwhat kind of person you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.04,0:07:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.66,0:07:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm going to tag along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.88,0:07:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The point is, you just need the location\Nof this person you're looking for, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.47,0:07:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you're a Detection-type Strega?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't call myself that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I can accomplish\Nsomething similar enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I need some information\Nto be able to visualize her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'm looking\Nfor a girl who's ten years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Flora.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's not lost, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. She's been captured by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The perpetrator is...\NI can guess, but I'm not sure yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I can do without that, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what about this girl's\Nlooks and personality?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.29,0:08:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:27.17,Sign Left DO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NAME\N\NNATIONALITY
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:27.17,Sign Left Mid DO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DATE OF BIRTH: 5/10        AGE\N\N\NGENDER: FEMALE        BLOOD TYPE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think we're good now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there's just one thing I want you\Nto promise me first. All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Promise you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.43,0:08:41.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever tell anyone\Nabout what's about to happen now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.56,0:08:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm going to get started,\Nso open up a map.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.73,0:08:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The bigger the better, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right. How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:06.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.96,0:09:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sylvia Lyyneheym!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.89,0:10:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sylvia Lyyneheym...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Queenvail Girls Academy's Rank #1.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Songstress and a Strega...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Using song as her medium,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.32,0:10:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she can transform her own image\Nin all kinds of ways.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.53,0:10:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her power is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}omnipotence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.01,0:10:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.60,0:10:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's the northern corner\Njust outside Rotlicht.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying Flora's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if I had more time to narrow it down,\NI could've given you a better idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.69,0:10:57.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, this is more than enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.53,0:11:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy I was able to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll be on my way now,\Nor my manager will give me an earful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold up a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.79,0:11:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind,\Ncould you give me your number?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.22,0:11:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone's hit on me\Nso blatantly in a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.18,0:11:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I wasn't hitting on you\Nor anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:27.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to thank you properly,\NMs. Lyyneheym.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:29.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can call me Sylvie!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:34.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's my private address,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so contact me anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.48,0:11:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I've been\Na little intrigued by you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Talking to you in person today,\Nthat intrigue is stronger now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.00,0:11:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, good luck to you, Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In my own humble way,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.09,0:11:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be praying\Nfor little Flora's safe return.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's great that you got a lead\Non Flora's whereabouts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But how did you\Nnarrow it down to this spot?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Uh... well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sorry, I can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, whatever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.82,0:12:25.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, let's head over there right now!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.66,0:12:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Both you and Ayato should stay away.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've got the final.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The final starts at noon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That gives us some time, doesn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, this time around,\NSasamiya's in the right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It would be too reckless\Nto go into the final like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:43.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You should rest as much as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ayato-senpai, Julis, we'll be fine!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.52,0:12:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're going to rescue Flora\Nno matter what!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Fine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.15,0:12:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}Then let's focus\Nall our energy on the final.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll go rescue Flora,\Nand you two will avenge us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All's well that ends well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\i1}They're counting on us,\Nas well, aren't they?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Though it's a bit too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.87,0:13:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No problem.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.21,0:13:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we can rescue Flora,\Nyou'll be able to use the Ser=Versta.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.09,0:13:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, as long as you get it done\Nin time, that is.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you have to be\Nsuch a buzzkill, Yabuki?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}- Just sayin', just sayin'...\N- I'm gonna kick your butt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.22,0:13:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Number 7, what's the situation?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Compliant, at least outwardly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shadow Star doesn't seem\Nto be on the move, either.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there was a totally suspicious-looking\Npunk digging around the joint.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.90,0:13:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as you know, the people\Nwho run the Rotlicht all hate my guts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm not sure how solid that intel is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What if someone crashes the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Play the hostage card.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't give a damn\Nif it's an expendable one.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.71,0:14:03.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's wrong?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently the party-crashers\Nhave just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This building used to be\Na fairly well-known casino,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but recently one of its\Ncustomers went berserk
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and totally trashed the place, I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That sounds scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not uncommon, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I hear they've stopped\Nconstruction for the last few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stopped it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:27.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then it's like\Na vacant house right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty sketchy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, why don't we\Ngo inside and check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.58,0:14:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B-But how are we gonna do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep an eye out for me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.22,0:14:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now we're in business!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, why don't we...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:03.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't anything hard core!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just used some tools\NI picked up online,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I've only ever\Ntried it out a few times.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:09.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was too easy for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.57,0:15:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The place seems to be deserted, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:24.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Upstairs or downstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I think\Nwe should all stick together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:31.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heartily second that motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm not a good brawler.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the part where you say,\N"I'm a man, leave it to me."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there is such a thing\Nas "right man, right job"!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:42.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I've done my due diligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.23,0:15:43.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Due diligence?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since I won't be of any use myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,all I have to do is call on someone\Nwho will be, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.16,0:15:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that... Is that a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's all this Mana\Nconcentrated around there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.08,0:15:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably Setting Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.21,0:16:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, looks like\Nwe are in the right place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?\NThat wasn't much of a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet even I can handle...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How many do you think there are?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.37,0:16:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this must be\Nautonomous-type power, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These guys can only execute\Nsimple commands for the most part!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They must've been ordered\Nto get rid of any intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's no reason\Nfor us to deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.59,0:16:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you cover me for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My legs...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}39-type Lux Ray Gun, Wolfdora...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.15,0:17:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Burst.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Strafe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Saya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I probably only have two\Nor three more shots left, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:27.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I think it's too soon to relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This could be endless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kirin, I know it's a little reckless,\Nbut we're going to charge in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I think that's our only choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.78,0:17:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell\Ndo you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just the man I've been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MacPhail-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:17:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.28,0:18:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damned Yabuki forced me to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now.\NWhat do you mean by "forced"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was ask you for a favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blackmailing as a negotiating tactic!\NIs that how you ask for favors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Threatening is more like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.42,0:18:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, MacPhail,\Ntake care of the rest, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.22,0:18:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.05,0:18:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you\Nto take care of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, best of luck, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hold up, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So Kirin... upstairs or downstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you think, Saya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.15,0:18:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I heard what's going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But even still...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I have to\Ntake on a role like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:54.09,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,COUNTDOWN TO THE FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:02.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We never did hear\Nfrom Saya and Kirin, did we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.57,0:19:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that look, Ayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.20,0:19:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to have friends\Nyou can trust, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The thing about me, Ayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flora... Everyone back home...\NThey mean everything to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.51,0:19:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I swore\NI'd do anything for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.59,0:19:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I always thought\Nthey were all I'd ever need.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But now that I think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,by doing that,\NI was only closing off the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have you as my, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,my partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that really hit home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.07,0:19:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Julis...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm not done\Nmaking more friends I can cherish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like Saya and Kirin, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.75,0:20:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I can believe\Nin them whole-heartedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's good, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, emerging from the east gate{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is Seidoukan Academy's\NAmagiri/Riessfeld team!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And from the west gate,\NArlequint Academy's AR-D/RM-C team!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.78,0:20:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We've seen all kinds of battles\Nover the last two weeks,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.74,0:20:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and now the Phoenix Festa\Nis down to its last battle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the final match!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, wow, I can't wait!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:51.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It really is mystifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Despite our situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.21,0:20:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I want to win this match\Nso badly, I can hardly stand it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.59,0:21:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.63,0:21:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.88,0:21:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,let's go for it all, you and I!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.55,0:21:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we take everything\Nwe've ever wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:13.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Without missing a single one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.27,0:21:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So we meet at last, Ayato Amagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.95,0:21:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have been looking forward to this day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I'm always hearing\Nabout you from my master,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.58,0:21:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I expect great things of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please trigger more exhilaration\Nin me than Kirin Toudou did!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately,\NI can't guarantee that I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But this match...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Victory will be ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.31,0:21:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}These surging emotions...\NI cannot hold them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.78,0:23:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ayato Amagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.99,0:23:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I have waited so long to battle you—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.79,0:23:35.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Be silent, you good-for-nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.50,0:23:40.04,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 20\NThe Phoenix Showdown
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.58,0:23:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}There isn't sufficient time during this\Npreview to waste on useless prattle.
